      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Bowled Over",
        "Client": "Hapless Trader",
        "Description": "Man, I cannot catch a break! I was making\r\nmy way through the Plains when I started\r\nhearing this, *boingy* *boingy* *boingy*\r\nnoise. Then suddenly two Volvidon appear\r\nout of nowhere and roll over my cart! To make\r\nmatters worse, any produce that didn\u0027t get\r\nsquashed was covered in their nasty spit!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Coup de boule",
        "Client": "Marchande malchanceuse",
        "Description": "Bon sang, mais \u00E7a devient une\r\nhabitude ! Je rentrais des Plaines,\r\nquand j\u0027ai commenc\u00E9 \u00E0 entendre de\r\ndr\u00F4les de bruits et c\u0027est l\u00E0 que\r\ndeux Volvidon sont sortis de nulle\r\npart et ont renvers\u00E9 mon chariot !\r\nToute ma marchandise est fichue !",
        "Target": "Chasser deux Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Capitombolo",
        "Client": "Mercante sfortunata",
        "Description": "Non ho mai pace! Stavo\r\ntornando dalle Piane e d\u0027un\r\ntratto sono apparsi due\r\nVolvidon che hanno rovesciato\r\nil mio carro. Le verdure che\r\nnon si sono ammaccate sono\r\nricoperte della sua saliva!",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Volvidon",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Umgehauen",
        "Client": "Gl\u00FCcklose H\u00E4ndlerin",
        "Description": "Mann, ich komm einfach nicht zur Ruhe!\r\nIch war auf dem Weg durch die Ebene, als\r\ndieses federnde Ger\u00E4usch anfing. Dann sind\r\nda aus dem Nichts pl\u00F6tzlich zwei Volvidon\r\nund \u00FCberrollen meinen Wagen! Zu allem \u00DCbel\r\nsind alle Erzeugnisse, die nicht zermatscht\r\nwurden, mit ihrem ekligen Speichel benetzt!",
        "Target": "Erjage zwei Volvidon.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Ojo con las bolas de bolos",
        "Client": "Mercader desafortunada",
        "Description": "\u00A1Qu\u00E9 desgracia! Sobreviv\u00ED a la\r\npersecuci\u00F3n de dos Volvidon\r\nfuriosos, pero, en la huida,\r\n\u00A1todos mis productos frescos\r\nacabaron tan chafados que no\r\nlos puedo vender! \u00A1Venga mis\r\nganancias perdidas!",
        "Target": "Caza 2 Volvidon",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0428\u0430\u0440\u044B",
        "Client": "\u041D\u0435\u0441\u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u043D\u0430\u044F \u0442\u043E\u0440\u0433\u043E\u0432\u043A\u0430",
        "Description": "\u041D\u0438 \u043C\u0438\u043D\u0443\u0442\u044B \u043F\u043E\u043A\u043E\u044F! \u042F \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u043B\u0430\u0441\u044C\r\n\u0447\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0437 \u0420\u0430\u0432\u043D\u0438\u043D\u044B, \u0438 \u0432\u0434\u0440\u0443\u0433 \u2014 \u043F\u0440\u044B\u0433,\r\n\u043F\u0440\u044B\u0433, \u043F\u0440\u044B\u0433! \u041F\u043E\u044F\u0432\u0438\u043B\u0438\u0441\u044C \u0434\u0432\u0430\r\n\u0412\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0432\u0438\u0434\u043E\u043D\u0430 \u0438 \u043F\u0440\u043E\u043A\u0430\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0438\u0441\u044C \u043F\u0440\u044F\u043C\u043E\r\n\u043F\u043E \u043C\u043E\u0435\u0439 \u043F\u043E\u0432\u043E\u0437\u043A\u0435! \u0410 \u0447\u0442\u043E \u043E\u043D\u0438 \u043D\u0435\r\n\u0440\u0430\u0437\u0434\u0430\u0432\u0438\u043B\u0438, \u0442\u043E \u0437\u0430\u043F\u043B\u0435\u0432\u0430\u043B\u0438!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C 2 \u0412\u043E\u043B\u044C\u0432\u0438\u0434\u043E\u043D\u043E\u0432",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
