      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Poobt\u0142ukiwane",
        "Client": "Pechowa handlarka",
        "Description": "Ci\u0105gle co\u015B mi si\u0119 przytrafia! Ostatnio\r\njecha\u0142am sobie przez R\u00F3wniny i nagle\r\ns\u0142ysz\u0119 takie boing! boing! boing!\r\nPatrz\u0119, a tu jak spod ziemi wyskakuj\u0105\r\ndwa Volvidony i przetaczaj\u0105 si\u0119 po\r\nmoim wozie! Wszystko albo pomia\u017Cd\u017Cone,\r\nalbo pokryte ich wstr\u0119tn\u0105 \u015Blin\u0105!",
        "Target": "Upoluj 2 Volvidony",
        "Fail": "Nagroda = 0 lub koniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Que bolada!",
        "Client": "Comerciante desafortunada",
        "Description": "Cara, eu n\u00E3o tenho paz! Eu tava andando\r\nnas Plan\u00EDcies quando comecei a ouvir um\r\nbarulho \u0022boing, boing, boing\u0022.\r\nDe repente, dois Volvidon aparecem do\r\nnada e rolaram sobre a minha carro\u00E7a!\r\nPra piorar, qualquer produto que n\u00E3o foi\r\nesmagado ficou coberto de baba nojenta!",
        "Target": "Cace 2 Volvidons",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
